Many construction companies, owners
of many buildings here in Sao Paulo,

24
00:01:28.710 --> 00:01:32.340
have capital to invest.

25
00:01:32.340 --> 00:01:36.650
I can't recall their names now.

26
00:01:36.650 --> 00:01:40.770
And so that the population stays
by their side, they have influence

27
00:01:40.770 --> 00:01:43.940
on the media so that it won't

28
00:01:43.940 --> 00:01:46.910
show news that go against them.

29
