A more recent example,

30
00:01:51.110 --> 00:01:55.020
I don't know if it's going to
be a problem to say it: Itaú.

31
00:01:55.020 --> 00:02:01.770
Itaú Bank is now privatizing
many places in the city,

32
00:02:01.770 --> 00:02:06.340
like squares, with the
government permission.

33
00:02:08.020 --> 00:02:13.570
There's this matter regarding
the real state speculation,

34
00:02:13.650 --> 00:02:16.540
which we from the movement
call real state corruption,

35
00:02:16.540 --> 00:02:20.770
that is, they're investing in
the city centre, making it

36
00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:23.820
a prime area, and so people
with less conditions...

37
00:02:23.820 --> 00:02:29.080
street dwellers, other dwellers

38
00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:34.220
end up having to leave the place,
which in theory is everyone's.

39
00:02:34.220 --> 00:02:38.820
Then what happens? Itaú sells an
image by refurbishing the centre,

40
00:02:38.820 --> 00:02:41.680
placing public equipments

41
